\"audio-player-tts__settings--current-speed-text uni-small-text\">1X</span> \n          <svg class=\"icon tts-chevron\">\n           <use xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260319-1641#tts-chevron\"></use>\n          </svg> </span></button>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"audio-player-tts__settings--voices uni-cta-text\">\n        <button class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-back\" aria-label=\"Click to go back\">\n         <svg class=\"icon tts-chevron\">\n          <use xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260319-1641#tts-chevron\"></use>\n         </svg>\n         <span>Voice</span>\n        </button>\n        <button class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-option audio-player-tts__settings-option--selected\"><span>Umbriel</span></button>\n        <button class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-option\"><span>Gacrux</span></button>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"audio-player-tts__settings--speeds uni-cta-text\">\n        <button class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-back\" aria-label=\"Click to go back\">\n         <svg class=\"icon tts-chevron\">\n          <use xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" href=\"/static/blogv2/images/icons.svg?version=pr20260319-1641#tts-chevron\"></use>\n         </svg>\n         <span>Speed</span>\n        </button>\n        <button class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-option\" data-speed=\"0.75\" aria-label=\"speed 0.75X\"><span>0.75X</span></button>\n        <button class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-option audio-player-tts__settings-option--selected\" data-speed=\"1\" aria-label=\"speed 1X\"><span>1X</span></button>\n        <button class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-option\" data-speed=\"1.5\" aria-label=\"speed 1.5X\"><span>1.5X</span></button>\n        <button class=\"audio-player-tts__settings-option\" data-speed=\"2\" aria-label=\"speed 2X\"><span>2X</span></button>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <!--article text-->\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;How 400+ campuses are putting AI to work&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"14zdh\" class=\"drop-cap\">In less than a year, more than 400 higher education institutions across all 50 states have joined the <a href=\"http://grow.google/edu\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI for Education Accelerator</a>, a no-cost program to help students, faculty and staff with AI and other job-ready skills. As part of the Accelerator, colleges and universities receive access to the <a href=\"https://grow.google/ai-professional-control/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Professional Certificate</a>, one of the first AI programs to receive a credit recommendation from the American Council on Education (ACE).</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"3jko7\">Helping students prepare for the workforce</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"b92kc\">The <a href=\"https://grow.google/ai-professional-control/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Professional Certificate</a>, built by Google experts with input from industry leading employers, equips students with the AI skills that employers are looking for. With a focus on practical skills that apply across industries, the program teaches students to solve everyday work challenges while potentially earning college credit toward their degree.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"81oui\">Across the country, hundreds of our partners, including The University of Texas System and Vanderbilt University, are already putting these resources into action.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"2868d\">For example, The Texas A&amp;M University System launched an AI Learnathon to provide AI training and tools to staff and faculty. Students at the University of Virginia who complete the AI Professional Certificate have an opportunity to put their skills to immediate use by partnering with local small businesses to help them integrate AI into their daily operations. And the University of Michigan is offering the AI Professional Certificate to all students, faculty, staff and alumni through their Center for Academic Innovation.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"c8m7c\">For more AI training, check out our <a href=\"http://grow.google/students\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AI videos for students</a> and our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLP7Bvyb3ap46BI2SOtXWZitbnAl7zpsU3\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini Faculty Fundamentals YouTube series</a>.</p>\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"f9osl\">Shaping the future of learning, together</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5snk1\">The <a href=\"https://grow.google/certificates-academic-institutions/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI for Education Accelerator</a> and the <a href=\"https://grow.google/ai-professional-control/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AI Professional Certificate</a> are part of <a href=\"https://blog.google/products-and-platforms/products/education/teacher-ai-literacy-training/\">our ongoing commitment to support the more than 6 million educators</a> who use our tools every day. By helping schools and faculty bring AI into the classroom, we’re making sure the next generation of graduates isn't just watching the AI shift happen, they’re making AI work for them.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"bjqn\">Accredited nonprofit colleges and universities can apply to join the Google AI for Education Accelerator at no cost at <a href=\"https://grow.google/certificates-academic-institutions/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">grow.google/edu</a>.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google 的 AI 教育加速器项目已扩展至 400 多所高等教育机构，为学生和教职员工提供符合行业标准的 AI 培训及专业认证。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google 的 AI 教育加速器项目已扩展至 400 多所高等教育机构，为学生和教职员工提供符合行业标准的 AI 培训及专业认证。",
  "summary": "本文重点介绍了 Google AI 教育加速器项目的快速普及，该项目目前已被美国 400 多所学院和大学采用。该计划为学术机构提供了获取 Google AI 专业认证的途径，并已获得美国教育委员会（ACE）的学分推荐。通过与德克萨斯大学系统和密歇根大学等大型高校合作，Google 旨在弥合学术学习与就业准备之间的差距，确保学生和教职员工能够掌握实用的、与行业相关的 AI 技能，并将其融入专业和学术环境中。",
